modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod increases the chances for eggs and feathers. Some nests will be vanilla rates while other have a chance to find a really good nest.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod increases the chances for [eggs](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-food/) and feathers. Some nests will be vanilla rates while other have a chance to find a really good nest. Increased eggs from 1 to possibly 3 eggs in a nest.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/wolfbain5/7dtd-a18/tree/master/better%20nests)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/14626-wolfbain5-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Wolfbain5](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/wolfbain5/)
